---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Contact Us — High School Sports Banquet Planning Resources" description="Get in touch with questions about banquet planning, custom centerpieces, or collaboration opportunities. We're here to help coaches and booster clubs plan better celebrations.">
  <div class="breadcrumbs">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <strong>Contact Us</strong>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Let's Talk About Your Athletic Celebration</h1>
      <p>Have a question about your banquet? Need help choosing the right centerpiece? We're here to help.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-wrapper" style="max-width:650px;margin:0 auto;">
        <p>We'd love to hear from you. Whether you have a question about planning your banquet, need help choosing the right centerpiece for your sport, or want to share your own tips — please reach out.</p>

        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> [your email here]<br />
        <strong>Response time:</strong> Usually within 24 hours</p>

        <h2>Common Inquiries</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom centerpiece orders and design questions</li>
          <li>Bulk orders for multiple sports or events</li>
          <li>Sponsorship or advertising opportunities</li>
          <li>Contributing content or sharing your event story</li>
        </ul>

        <p>For urgent questions about an upcoming event, please mention the event date in your message so we can prioritize your request.</p>

        <div class="product-note">
          <p><strong>🏆 Looking for centerpieces?</strong> Browse our collection of custom 3D printed sports centerpieces.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/collections/all" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">Shop Centerpieces →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

